            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, add the <strong>fine egg noodles </strong>to a pot and cover with <strong>boiled water </strong>until fully submerged</p>\n<p>Bring to the boil over a high heat and cook for 4-5 min or until tender with a slight bite</p>\n<p>Once cooked, drain and rinse under <strong>cold water</strong> then set aside until they're completely drained</p>",
